---
title: Caesar-Inspired Saucy Grilled Salmon and Shrimp with Potato Salad and Asparagus
description: This long-weekend grill sauce is inspired by a Canadian classic drink: the Caesar! Grilled salmon and shrimp are slathered and dipped in the classic flavours of horseradish, hot sauce and tomato. Asparagus and creamy potato salad are the perfect pairing!
